1. [Error] No compiler is provided in this environment. Perhaps you are running on a JRE rather than a JDK?
Solution : Add JDK
Steps : Eclipse Preferences 
> Java 
> Installed JREs 
> (Uncheck JRE) Add 
> JRE Home (Directory...) 
> Choose path till jdk (e.g. : "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_66") 
> Finish
> Check JDK
> Apply and Okay

2. How to tell the "Team Synchronizing" to ignore some files :
Solution : Eclipse Preferences 
> Team
> Ignored Resources
> Add Pattern
> Ok > Apply > Ok
